About.title: About Me
About.description:
Hello! I'm a Software Engineer and Computer Science student at UofT. I think tech is cool and I like to build things.
I have a wealth of professional work experience in the field of software development and have worked with a variety of technologies and frameworks.
Outside of work, I like to cook, play video games, and spend time with my family and friends.
